 you log in, we will also set up several cookies to save your login information and your screen display choices. Login cookies last for two days, and screen options cookies last for a year. If you select &quot;Remember Me&quot;, your login will persist for two weeks. If you log out of your account, the login cookies will be removed.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you edit or publish an article, an additional cookie will be saved in your browser. This cookie includes no personal data and simply indicates the post ID of the article you just edited. It expires after 1 day.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Embedded content from other websites</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong class=\"privacy-policy-tutorial\">Suggested text: </strong>Articles on this site may include embedded content (e.g. videos, images, articles, etc.). Embedded content from other websites behaves in the exact same way as if the visitor has visited the other website.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>These websites may collect data about you, use cookies, embed additional third-party tracking, and monitor your interaction with that embedded content, including tracking your interaction with the embedded content if you have an account and are logged in to that website.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Who we share your data with</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong class=\"privacy-policy-tutorial\">Suggested text: </strong>If you request a password reset, your IP address will be included in the reset email.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How long we retain your data</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong class=\"privacy-policy-tutorial\">Suggested text: </strong>If you leave a comment, the comment and its metadata are retained indefinitely. This is so we can recognize and approve any follow-up comments automatically instead of holding them in a moderation queue.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For users that register on our website (if any), we also store the personal information they provide in their user profile. All users can see, edit, or delete their personal information at any time (except they cannot change their username). Website administrators can also see and edit that information.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What rights you have over your data</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong class=\"privacy-policy-tutorial\">Suggested text: </strong>If you have an account on this site, or have left comments, you can request to receive an exported file of the personal data we hold about you, including any data you have provided to us. You can also request that we erase any personal data we hold about you. This does not include any data we are obliged to keep for administrative, legal, or security purposes.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Where your data is sent</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong class=\"privacy-policy-tutorial\">Suggested text: </strong>Visitor comments may be checked through an automated spam detection service.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n','Privacy Policy','','trash','closed','open','','privacy-policy__trashed','','','2026-07-01 20:40:49','2026-07-01 20:40:49','',0,'http://localhost:8881/?page_id=3',0,'page','',0),(12,1,'2026-07-02 11:29:44','2026-07-02 11:29:44','','Home','','trash','closed','closed','','home__trashed','','','2026-07-02 11:29:44','2026-07-02 11:29:44','',0,'http://localhost:8881/?page_id=6',0,'page','',0),(13,1,'2026-07-02 15:32:46','2026-07-02 15:32:46','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Andalusian Rescue Centre for Horses (El Centro Andalusi de Rescate de Caballos) has now been recognised as Utilidad Publica by the Spanish Ministry of the Interior. It follows many years of tireless work rescuing abused and abandoned horses, ponies and donkeys and rehabilitating and rehoming them, since ARCH was founded in 2009. This reflects the growing awareness of the importance of animal welfare in Spain as well as the tangible impact of stronger animal protection laws. ARCH has close links with the authorities, working with SEPRONA and the local Police. It has a government contract to rehome retiring cavalry horses, and is contracted to take in abandoned equines in Alhaurin el Grande. The charity plays an active role in the community, educating the younger generation in equine care, welcoming school visits and hosting open days.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ARCH President and founder of the charity, Jill Newman-Rogers commented “This is a very important milestone for ARCH, few animal charities are granted the title of Utilidad Publica. With our new status we anticipate a greater intake of equines at risk, so donations are essential for our work, as are our dedicated team of volunteers. Please support El Centro Andalusi de Rescate de Caballos and consider a lasting legacy by including us in your Will.”</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":109,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/horseinsuit2-1548783616-1024x669.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-109\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','RECOGNITION FOR YEARS OF EFFORT','','publish','open','open','','heres-a-little-post','','','2026-07-03 14:43:40','2026-07-03 14:43:40','',0,'http://localhost:8881/?p=7',0,'post','',0),(17,1,'2026-07-02 10:59:54','2026-07-02 10:59:54','{\"version\": 3, \"isGlobalStylesUserThemeJSON\": true }','Custom Styles','','publish','closed','closed','','wp-global-styles-arch-theme','','','2026-07-02 10:59:54','2026-07-02 10:59:54','',0,'http://localhost:8881/2026/07/02/wp-global-styles-arch-theme/',0,'wp_global_styles','',0),(18,1,'2026-07-02 11:01:34','2026-07-02 11:01:34','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Here is some horsey info</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Test Horsey','','trash','closed','closed','','test-horsey__trashed','','','2026-07-02 11:01:34','2026-07-02 11:01:34','',0,'http://localhost:8881/?post_type=equine&amp;p=18',0,'equine','',0),(24,1,'2026-07-02 11:29:18','2026-07-02 11:29:18','','home-content','','trash','closed','closed','','home-content__trashed','','','2026-07-03 15:01:15','2026-07-03 15:01:15','',0,'http://localhost:8881/?page_id=24',0,'page','',0),(28,1,'2026-07-02 12:34:40','2026-07-02 12:34:40','','Revoltosa','','publish','closed','closed','','horsey','','','2026-07-05 14:39:10','2026-07-05 14:39:10','',0,'http://localhost:8881/?post_type=equine&#038;p=28',0,'equine','',0),(38,1,'2026-07-02 14:41:48','2026-07-02 14:41:48','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For little bangs and bigger bangs, whilst they heal</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Bandages','','publish','closed','closed','','bandages','','','2026-07-02 14:41:48','2026-07-02 14:41:48','',0,'http://localhost:8881/?post_type=wishlist_item&amp;p=38',0,'wishlist_item','',0),(39,1,'2026-07-02 14:42:41','2026-07-02 14:42:41','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We’d love some extra tack!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Halter &amp; Lead Rope','','publish','closed','closed','','halter-lead-rope','','','2026-07-02 14:42:41','2026-07-02 14:42:41','',0,'http://localhost:8881/?post_type=wishlist_item&amp;p=39',0,'wishlist_item','',0),(40,1,'2026-07-02 14:43:40','2026-07-02 14:43:40','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Dental work can be expensive, especially for our older residents</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Dental Revision','','publish','closed','closed','','dental-revision','','','2026-07-02 14:43:40','2026-07-02 14:43:40','',0,'http://localhost:8881/?post_type=wishlist_item&amp;p=40',0,'wishlist_item','',0),(42,1,'2026-07-02 14:44:43','2026-07-02 14:44:43','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For that Salon-Fresh look!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Shampoo','','publish','closed','closed','','shampoo','','','2026-07-02 14:44:43','2026-07-02 14:44:43','',0,'http://localhost:8881/?post_type=wishlist_item&amp;p=42',0,'wishlist_item','',0),(44,1,'2026-07-02 14:52:27','2026-07-02 14:52:27','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Not glamourous but definitely necessary!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Deworming','','publish','closed','closed','','deworming','','','2026-07-02 14:52:27','2026-07-02 14:52:27','',0,'http://localhost:8881/?post_type=wishlist_item&amp;p=44',0,'wishlist_item','',0),(45,1,'2026-07-02 14:53:23','2026-07-02 14:53:23','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We tried giving our residents fly swats, but spray is better!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Fly Spray','','publish','closed','closed','','fly-spray','','','2026-07-02 14:53:23','2026-07-02 14:53:23','',0,'http://localhost:8881/?post_type=wishlist_item&amp;p=45',0,'wishlist_item','',0),(46,1,'2026-07-02 15:00:28','2026-07-02 15:00:28','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our newest arrival is a long-legged colt, jealously guarded by his mum Victoria. After a few worrying days, when we were not sure he would survive, the little man is now up and about and looking well. We have named him Lucero, which means bright or shining star. Little Luz de Luna in the adjoining paddock is dying to make friends but Victoria is very possessive and so far the babies have only touched noses briefly!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":112,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/87dbe576f48e5125c8ae5759dbf0b01d-4215696547.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-112\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->','A STAR IS BORN','','publish','open','open','','this-is-a-test-post','','','2026-07-03 14:44:13','2026-07-03 14:44:13','',0,'http://localhost:8881/?p=46',0,'post','',0),(51,1,'2026-07-02 15:35:09','2026-07-02 15:35:09','','ChilliFM','','publish','closed','closed','','chillifm','','','2026-07-03 15:14:47','2026-07-03 15:14:47','',0,'http://localhost:8881/?post_type=sponsor&#038;p=51',0,'sponsor','',0),(53,1,'2026-07-02 15:38:07','2026-07-02 15:38:07','','SolarSurf','','publish','closed','closed','','solarsurf','','','2026-07-03 15:14:36','2026-07-03 15:14:36','',0,'http://localhost:8881/?post_type=sponsor&#038;p=53',0,'sponsor','',0),(55,1,'2026-07-02 15:40:41','2026-07-02 15:40:41','','Saracen Horse Feeds','','publish','closed','closed','','saracen-horse-feeds','','','2026-07-03 15:14:25','2026-07-03 15:14:25','',0,'http://localhost:8881/?post_type=sponsor&#038;p=55',0,'sponsor','',0),(57,1,'2026-07-02 15:42:25','2026-07-02 15:42:25','','Mediterranean Homes','','publish','closed','closed','','mediterranean-homes','','','2026-07-03 15:14:15','2026-07-03 15:14:15','',0,'http://localhost:8881/?post_type=sponsor&#038;p=57',0,'sponsor','',0),(59,1,'2026-07-02 15:43:41','2026-07-02 15:43:41','','Jaime Ocaña Ortiz','','publish','closed','closed','','jaime-ocana-ortiz','','','2026-07-03 15:14:06','2026-07-03 15:14:06','',0,'http://localhost:8881/?post_type=sponsor&#038;p=59',0,'sponsor','',0),(61,1,'2026-07-02 15:44:51','2026-07-02 15:44:51','','Fruitful Hills','','publish','closed','closed','','fruitful-hills','','','2026-07-03 15:13:54','2026-07-03 15:13:54','',0,'http://localhost:8881/?post_type=sponsor&#038;p=61',0,'sponsor','',0),(64,1,'2026-07-02 20:50:43','2026-07-02 20:50:43','','Business Horse','','publish','closed','closed','','business-horse','','','2026-07-04 20:26:22','2026-07-04 20:26:22','',0,'http://localhost:8881/?post_type=equine&#038;p=64',0,'equine','',0),(68,1,'2026-07-02 20:52:30','2026-07-02 20:52:30','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>At our rescue centre just outside Málaga, we try to rehome every rescue once they\'re suitably rehabilitated.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Adoption','','publish','closed','closed','','page-adoption-php','','','2026-07-08 19:49:05','2026-07-08 19:49:05','',0,'http://localhost:8881/?page_id=68',0,'page','',0),(69,1,'2026-07-05 19:43:59','2026-07-03 14:27:33','','Contact','','publish','closed','closed','','contact','','','2026-07-05 19:43:59','2026-07-05 19:43:59','',0,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/2026/07/03/contact/',7,'nav_menu_item','',0),(71,1,'2026-07-05 19:43:59','2026-07-03 14:27:33','','Home','','publish','closed','closed','','home','','','2026-07-05 19:43:59','2026-07-05 19:43:59','',0,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/2026/07/03/home/',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(89,1,'2026-07-03 12:28:14','2026-07-03 12:28:14','','News','','publish','closed','closed','','news','','','2026-07-03 14:34:26','2026-07-03 14:34:26','',0,'http://localhost:8881/?page_id=89',0,'page','',0),(91,1,'2026-07-01 20:40:51','2026-07-01 20:40:51','<!-- wp:page-list /-->','Navigation','','publish','closed','closed','','navigation-2','','','2026-07-01 20:40:51','2026-07-01 20:40:51','',0,'http://localhost:8881/2026/07/01/navigation/',0,'wp_navigation','',0),(98,1,'2026-07-05 19:43:59','2026-07-03 14:28:08',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','',98,'','','2026-07-05 19:43:59','2026-07-05 19:43:59','',0,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/2026/07/03/',6,'nav_menu_item','',0),(102,1,'2026-07-03 14:34:25','2026-07-03 14:34:25','','News','','inherit','closed','closed','','89-revision-v1','','','2026-07-03 14:34:25','2026-07-03 14:34:25','',89,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/?p=102',0,'revision','',0),(103,1,'2026-07-03 14:34:30','2026-07-03 14:34:30','<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Who we are</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong class=\"privacy-policy-tutorial\">Suggested text: </strong>Our website address is: https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Comments</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong class=\"privacy-policy-tutorial\">Suggested text: </strong>When visitors leave comments on the site we collect the data shown in the comments form, and also the visitor&#8217;s IP address and browser user agent string to help spam detection.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>An anonymized string created from your email address (also called a hash) may be provided to the Gravatar service to see if you are using it. The Gravatar service privacy policy is available here: https://automattic.com/privacy/. After approval of your comment, your profile picture is visible to the public in the context of your comment.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Media</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong class=\"privacy-policy-tutorial\">Suggested text: </strong>If you upload images to the website, you should avoid uploading images with embedded location data (EXIF GPS) included. Visitors to the website can download and extract any location data from images on the website.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Cookies</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong class=\"privacy-policy-tutorial\">Suggested text: </strong>If you leave a comment on our site you may opt-in to saving your name, email address and website in cookies. These are for your convenience so that you do not have to fill in your details again when you leave another comment. These cookies will last for one year.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you visit our login page, we will set a temporary cookie to determine if your browser accepts cookies. This cookie contains no personal data and is discarded when you close your browser.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When you log in, we will also set up several cookies to save your login information and your screen display choices. Login cookies last for two days, and screen options cookies last for a year. If you select &quot;Remember Me&quot;, your login will persist for two weeks. If you log out of your account, the login cookies will be removed.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you edit or publish an article, an additional cookie will be saved in your browser. This cookie includes no personal data and simply indicates the post ID of the article you just edited. It expires after 1 day.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Embedded content from other websites</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong class=\"privacy-policy-tutorial\">Suggested text: </strong>Articles on this site may include embedded content (e.g. videos, images, articles, etc.). Embedded content from other websites behaves in the exact same way as if the visitor has visited the other website.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>These websites may collect data about you, use cookies, embed additional third-party tracking, and monitor your interaction with that embedded content, including tracking your interaction with the embedded content if you have an account and are logged in to that website.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Who we share your data with</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong class=\"privacy-policy-tutorial\">Suggested text: </strong>If you request a password reset, your IP address will be included in the reset email.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How long we retain your data</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong class=\"privacy-policy-tutorial\">Suggested text: </strong>If you leave a comment, the comment and its metadata are retained indefinitely. This is so we can recognize and approve any follow-up comments automatically instead of holding them in a moderation queue.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For users that register on our website (if any), we also store the personal information they provide in their user profile. All users can see, edit, or delete their personal information at any time (except they cannot change their username). Website administrators can also see and edit that information.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What rights you have over your data</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong class=\"privacy-policy-tutorial\">Suggested text: </strong>If you have an account on this site, or have left comments, you can request to receive an exported file of the personal data we hold about you, including any data you have provided to us. You can also request that we erase any personal data we hold about you. This does not include any data we are obliged to keep for administrative, legal, or security purposes.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Where your data is sent</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong class=\"privacy-policy-tutorial\">Suggested text: </strong>Visitor comments may be checked through an automated spam detection service.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n','Privacy Policy','','inherit','closed','closed','','3-revision-v1','','','2026-07-03 14:34:30','2026-07-03 14:34:30','',3,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/?p=103',0,'revision','',0),(104,1,'2026-07-03 14:34:33','2026-07-03 14:34:33','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>...or something like this:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\">\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n</blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Sample Page','','inherit','closed','closed','','2-revision-v1','','','2026-07-03 14:34:33','2026-07-03 14:34:33','',2,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/?p=104',0,'revision','',0),(105,1,'2026-07-03 14:35:07','2026-07-03 14:35:07','','home-content','','inherit','closed','closed','','24-revision-v1','','','2026-07-03 14:35:07','2026-07-03 14:35:07','',24,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/?p=105',0,'revision','',0),(109,1,'2026-07-03 14:43:28','2026-07-03 14:43:28','','horseinsuit2-1548783616','','inherit','open','closed','','horseinsuit2-1548783616','','','2026-07-03 14:43:28','2026-07-03 14:43:28','',13,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/horseinsuit2-1548783616.jpeg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(110,1,'2026-07-03 14:43:33','2026-07-03 14:43:33','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Andalusian Rescue Centre for Horses (El Centro Andalusi de Rescate de Caballos) has now been recognised as Utilidad Publica by the Spanish Ministry of the Interior. It follows many years of tireless work rescuing abused and abandoned horses, ponies and donkeys and rehabilitating and rehoming them, since ARCH was founded in 2009. This reflects the growing awareness of the importance of animal welfare in Spain as well as the tangible impact of stronger animal protection laws. ARCH has close links with the authorities, working with SEPRONA and the local Police. It has a government contract to rehome retiring cavalry horses, and is contracted to take in abandoned equines in Alhaurin el Grande. The charity plays an active role in the community, educating the younger generation in equine care, welcoming school visits and hosting open days.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ARCH President and founder of the charity, Jill Newman-Rogers commented “This is a very important milestone for ARCH, few animal charities are granted the title of Utilidad Publica. With our new status we anticipate a greater intake of equines at risk, so donations are essential for our work, as are our dedicated team of volunteers. Please support El Centro Andalusi de Rescate de Caballos and consider a lasting legacy by including us in your Will.”</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":97,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/unicorn-pictures-8wovjd42zorkt574-826963799-1024x1024.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-97\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','RECOGNITION FOR YEARS OF EFFORT','','inherit','closed','closed','','13-revision-v1','','','2026-07-03 14:43:33','2026-07-03 14:43:33','',13,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/?p=110',0,'revision','',0),(111,1,'2026-07-03 14:43:40','2026-07-03 14:43:40','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Andalusian Rescue Centre for Horses (El Centro Andalusi de Rescate de Caballos) has now been recognised as Utilidad Publica by the Spanish Ministry of the Interior. It follows many years of tireless work rescuing abused and abandoned horses, ponies and donkeys and rehabilitating and rehoming them, since ARCH was founded in 2009. This reflects the growing awareness of the importance of animal welfare in Spain as well as the tangible impact of stronger animal protection laws. ARCH has close links with the authorities, working with SEPRONA and the local Police. It has a government contract to rehome retiring cavalry horses, and is contracted to take in abandoned equines in Alhaurin el Grande. The charity plays an active role in the community, educating the younger generation in equine care, welcoming school visits and hosting open days.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ARCH President and founder of the charity, Jill Newman-Rogers commented “This is a very important milestone for ARCH, few animal charities are granted the title of Utilidad Publica. With our new status we anticipate a greater intake of equines at risk, so donations are essential for our work, as are our dedicated team of volunteers. Please support El Centro Andalusi de Rescate de Caballos and consider a lasting legacy by including us in your Will.”</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":109,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/horseinsuit2-1548783616-1024x669.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-109\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','RECOGNITION FOR YEARS OF EFFORT','','inherit','closed','closed','','13-revision-v1','','','2026-07-03 14:43:40','2026-07-03 14:43:40','',13,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/?p=111',0,'revision','',0),(112,1,'2026-07-03 14:44:01','2026-07-03 14:44:01','','87dbe576f48e5125c8ae5759dbf0b01d-4215696547','','inherit','open','closed','','87dbe576f48e5125c8ae5759dbf0b01d-4215696547','','','2026-07-03 14:44:01','2026-07-03 14:44:01','',46,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/87dbe576f48e5125c8ae5759dbf0b01d-4215696547.jpeg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(113,1,'2026-07-03 14:44:13','2026-07-03 14:44:13','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our newest arrival is a long-legged colt, jealously guarded by his mum Victoria. After a few worrying days, when we were not sure he would survive, the little man is now up and about and looking well. We have named him Lucero, which means bright or shining star. Little Luz de Luna in the adjoining paddock is dying to make friends but Victoria is very possessive and so far the babies have only touched noses briefly!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":112,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/87dbe576f48e5125c8ae5759dbf0b01d-4215696547.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-112\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->','A STAR IS BORN','','inherit','closed','closed','','46-revision-v1','','','2026-07-03 14:44:13','2026-07-03 14:44:13','',46,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/?p=113',0,'revision','',0),(114,1,'2026-07-03 14:44:38','2026-07-03 14:44:38','','Simba-head-1','','inherit','open','closed','','simba-head-1','','','2026-07-03 14:44:38','2026-07-03 14:44:38','',9,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Simba-head-1.jpeg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(115,1,'2026-07-03 14:44:46','2026-07-03 14:44:46','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ARCH representatives recently attended a convention at the University of Granada to discuss the new animal laws, organised by Servicios Juridicos Nazaries. There were attendees from other rescue organisations and our Animal Rights lawyer Aritz Toribio. At the end of the discussion certificates were presented to recognise the work of several participants, including ARCH president Jill Newman-Rogers who has “devoted her entire life to helping horses”.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":114,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Simba-head-1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-114\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pictured with Jill are Animal Rights lawyer Aritz Toribio,&nbsp;José Otero Cobos (SEPRONA) and Tania Vázquez Muiña (University of Granada)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','FIGHTING FOR JUSTICE','','inherit','closed','closed','','9-revision-v1','','','2026-07-03 14:44:46','2026-07-03 14:44:46','',9,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/?p=115',0,'revision','',0),(116,1,'2026-07-03 14:45:13','2026-07-03 14:45:13','','horsey 2','','inherit','open','closed','','horsey-2','','','2026-07-03 14:45:13','2026-07-03 14:45:13','',1,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/horsey-2.jpeg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(117,1,'2026-07-03 14:45:16','2026-07-03 14:45:16','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start writing!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Hello world!','','inherit','closed','closed','','1-revision-v1','','','2026-07-03 14:45:16','2026-07-03 14:45:16','',1,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/?p=117',0,'revision','',0),(118,1,'2026-07-03 14:50:30','2026-07-03 14:50:30','','Torero9','','inherit','open','closed','','torero9','','','2026-07-03 14:50:30','2026-07-03 14:50:30','',24,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Torero9.jpeg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(119,1,'2026-07-03 14:52:01','2026-07-03 14:52:01','','home-content','','inherit','closed','closed','','24-revision-v1','','','2026-07-03 14:52:01','2026-07-03 14:52:01','',24,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/?p=119',0,'revision','',0),(122,1,'2026-07-03 14:59:38','2026-07-03 14:59:38','','home-content','','inherit','closed','closed','','24-autosave-v1','','','2026-07-03 14:59:38','2026-07-03 14:59:38','',24,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/?p=122',0,'revision','',0),(123,1,'2026-07-03 15:01:33','2026-07-03 15:01:33','','home-content','','publish','closed','closed','','home-content','','','2026-07-06 20:02:47','2026-07-06 20:02:47','',0,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/?page_id=123',0,'page','',0),(124,1,'2026-07-03 15:01:15','2026-07-03 15:01:15','','home-content','','inherit','closed','closed','','24-revision-v1','','','2026-07-03 15:01:15','2026-07-03 15:01:15','',24,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/?p=124',0,'revision','',0),(125,1,'2026-07-03 15:01:33','2026-07-03 15:01:33','','home-content','','inherit','closed','closed','','123-revision-v1','','','2026-07-03 15:01:33','2026-07-03 15:01:33','',123,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/?p=125',0,'revision','',0),(126,1,'2026-07-03 15:04:31','2026-07-03 15:04:31','','Pam','','publish','closed','closed','','pam-jim','','','2026-07-04 21:14:37','2026-07-04 21:14:37','',0,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/?post_type=equine&#038;p=126',0,'equine','',0),(127,1,'2026-07-03 15:03:47','2026-07-03 15:03:47','','MAM 14 KH0343 01','Contentin Donkey And Foal Standing In Pasture France','inherit','open','closed','','mam-14-kh0343-01','','','2026-07-03 15:03:47','2026-07-03 15:03:47','',126,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/mam-14-kh0343-01p-3597089979.jpeg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(128,1,'2026-07-03 15:05:43','2026-07-03 15:05:43','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Torero','','publish','closed','closed','','torero','','','2026-07-06 11:16:32','2026-07-06 11:16:32','',0,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/?post_type=equine&#038;p=128',0,'equine','',0),(129,1,'2026-07-03 15:13:32','2026-07-03 15:13:32','','big-Cortijo-Fruitful-Hills','','inherit','open','closed','','big-cortijo-fruitful-hills','','','2026-07-03 15:13:32','2026-07-03 15:13:32','',61,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/big-Cortijo-Fruitful-Hills.jpeg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(130,1,'2026-07-03 15:13:32','2026-07-03 15:13:32','','Jaime-Ocana-Ortiz-farrier','','inherit','open','closed','','jaime-ocana-ortiz-farrier','','','2026-07-03 15:13:32','2026-07-03 15:13:32','',61,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Jaime-Ocana-Ortiz-farrier.jpeg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(131,1,'2026-07-03 15:13:33','2026-07-03 15:13:33','','wp-support-specialists-1','','inherit','open','closed','','wp-support-specialists-1','','','2026-07-03 15:13:33','2026-07-03 15:13:33','',61,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/wp-support-specialists-1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(132,1,'2026-07-03 15:13:33','2026-07-03 15:13:33','','logo-solarsurf','','inherit','open','closed','','logo-solarsurf','','','2026-07-03 15:13:33','2026-07-03 15:13:33','',61,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/logo-solarsurf.webp',0,'attachment','image/webp',0),(133,1,'2026-07-03 15:13:34','2026-07-03 15:13:34','','saracen-1','','inherit','open','closed','','saracen-1','','','2026-07-03 15:13:34','2026-07-03 15:13:34','',61,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/saracen-1.jpeg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(134,1,'2026-07-03 15:13:34','2026-07-03 15:13:34','','mediterranean-homes-1432718-3432747390','','inherit','open','closed','','mediterranean-homes-1432718-3432747390','','','2026-07-03 15:13:34','2026-07-03 15:13:34','',61,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/mediterranean-homes-1432718-3432747390.jpeg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(135,1,'2026-07-03 15:13:34','2026-07-03 15:13:34','','Chilli-FM','','inherit','open','closed','','chilli-fm','','','2026-07-03 15:13:34','2026-07-03 15:13:34','',61,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Chilli-FM.webp',0,'attachment','image/webp',0),(138,1,'2026-07-03 15:51:09','2026-07-03 15:51:09','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To make an easy online payment we have Donorbox to handle bank card payments for single and recurring contributions. (1.75% reduced payment processing fee for charities)<br><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Online Card Payment','','trash','closed','closed','','online-card-payment__trashed','','','2026-07-03 16:00:49','2026-07-03 16:00:49','',0,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/?post_type=donation_method&#038;p=138',0,'donation_method','',0),(139,1,'2026-07-03 15:52:33','2026-07-03 15:52:33','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We are registered as a charity with PayPal and so receive reduced processing fees. (1.99% + $0.49 per transaction)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our PayPal address is&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:info@horserescuespain.org\">info@horserescuespain.org</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Or click the following link if you are already logged into Paypal.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Paypal','','publish','closed','closed','','paypal-infohorserescuespain-org','','','2026-07-03 15:58:52','2026-07-03 15:58:52','',0,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/?post_type=donation_method&#038;p=139',0,'donation_method','',0),(140,1,'2026-07-03 15:54:15','2026-07-03 15:54:15','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Every donation </strong>we receive goes <strong>directly to the equines</strong> at ARCH. With your help we can ensure each rescued horse, donkey and pony receives the treatment and rehabilitation they so desperately need.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>By making this donation, you acknowledge that it is a voluntary and irrevocable contribution. Donations received are non-refundable and will be used in full for the purposes of Centro Andalusí de Rescate de Caballos (ARCH).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ARCH is a non-profit organisation, <strong>registered with the Andalusian Regional Government</strong> (Junta de Andalucía) with <strong>number 8448</strong> and declared of benefit to the public [utilidad pública] on 25 March 2026, which means that all Spanish tax payers can claim their donation against tax.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The most cost efficient way to donate is via direct bank transfer to our bank account.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Donate','','publish','closed','closed','','donations','','','2026-07-05 14:15:37','2026-07-05 14:15:37','',0,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/?page_id=140',0,'page','',0),(141,1,'2026-07-03 15:54:15','2026-07-03 15:54:15','','Donations','','inherit','closed','closed','','140-revision-v1','','','2026-07-03 15:54:15','2026-07-03 15:54:15','',140,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/?p=141',0,'revision','',0),(142,1,'2026-07-03 15:56:08','2026-07-03 15:56:08','','Donate','','inherit','closed','closed','','140-revision-v1','','','2026-07-03 15:56:08','2026-07-03 15:56:08','',140,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/?p=142',0,'revision','',0),(143,1,'2026-07-03 15:56:34','2026-07-03 15:56:34','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Every donation we receive goes directly to the equines at ARCH.<br>With your help we can ensure each rescued horse, donkey and pony receives the treatment and rehabilitation they so desperately need.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>By making this donation, you acknowledge that it is a voluntary and irrevocable contribution. Donations received are non-refundable and will be used in full for the purposes of Centro Andalusí de Rescate de Caballos (ARCH).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ARCH is a non-profit organisation, registered with the Andalusian Regional Government (Junta de Andalucía) with number 8448 and declared of benefit to the public [utilidad pública] on 25 March 2026, which means that all Spanish tax payers can claim their donation against tax.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The most cost efficient way to donate is via direct bank transfer to our bank account.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Donate','','inherit','closed','closed','','140-revision-v1','','','2026-07-03 15:56:34','2026-07-03 15:56:34','',140,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/?p=143',0,'revision','',0),(145,1,'2026-07-03 15:59:55','2026-07-03 15:59:55','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We have a teaming account for micro-donations of just €1 per month. We would love it if every one of our supporters in Europe would consider becoming a Teamer as it provides a steady stream of funding and the payment processing is free!. Unfortunately, Teaming is currently not available outside Europe.<br><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Teaming','','publish','closed','closed','','teaming','','','2026-07-03 15:59:56','2026-07-03 15:59:56','',0,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/?post_type=donation_method&#038;p=145',0,'donation_method','',0),(146,1,'2026-07-03 16:00:56','2026-07-03 16:00:56','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We rely on income from our ARCH Charity Shop in Alhaurín el Grande, donations of quality used items can be made by contacting the shop directly.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br>If you are having a clear out, downsizing or moving, please consider donating good quality items that you no longer need to the ARCH Charity Shop, as they are an invaluable source of funding. Drop off your goods at the shop in Alhaurín el Grande during shop opening hours (Mondays to Fridays 10 a.m. to 3 p.m., Saturdays 10 a.m to 2 p.m.) or contact us if you want us to arrange a collection, <a href=\"mailto:shop@horserescuespain.org\">shop@horserescuespain.org</a>.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Charity Shop items','','publish','closed','closed','','online-card-payment','','','2026-07-06 20:09:26','2026-07-06 20:09:26','',0,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/?post_type=donation_method&#038;p=146',0,'donation_method','',0),(148,1,'2026-07-03 16:05:12','2026-07-03 16:05:12','','UGRA = Union of Breeders of the Andalusian Donkey','','publish','closed','closed','','ugra-union-of-breeders-of-the-andalusian-donkey','','','2026-07-03 16:05:12','2026-07-03 16:05:12','',0,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/?post_type=sponsor&#038;p=148',0,'sponsor','',0),(149,1,'2026-07-03 16:05:09','2026-07-03 16:05:09','','UGRA-logo','','inherit','open','closed','','ugra-logo','','','2026-07-03 16:05:09','2026-07-03 16:05:09','',148,'https://rainycrowd.s3-tastewp.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/UGRA-logo.jpeg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(151,1,'2026-07-04 13:35:56','2026-07-04 13:35:56','','Volunteer with Us','','publish','closed','closed','','volunteer','','','2026-07-05 17:13:36','2026-07-05 17:13:36','',0,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?page_id=151',0,'page','',0),(152,1,'2026-07-04 13:35:56','2026-07-04 13:35:56','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We rely on the support of animal lovers across the globe, and it is with your help that we continue to provide relief to horses, donkeys and ponies in need.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Enjoy some meaningful work at the rescue centre. Donate a few hours of your time to help us groom, feed and muck out the paddocks – there is always plenty to do.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our&nbsp;<strong>volunteer hours</strong>&nbsp;are:<br><strong>Mornings</strong><em><br></em>Monday to Friday – 8:30am to 11am<br>Saturday and Sunday – 9am to 11am<br>In addition, on the 1st Sunday of every month (except July + August) we need volunteers to show our visitors around from 10am to 2pm (10 to 12 or 12 to 2)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Evenings</strong><br>Times differ seasonally, usually a 2hr shift between 6pm and 9pm</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Please note that&nbsp;<strong>we do not have accommodation</strong>&nbsp;so volunteers from further afield would need to arrange their own accommodation and transport.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>If you would like to volunteer at ARCH could you please, for your initial visit to the stables, come either on a Wednesday or Saturday between 9.00 and 11.00 a.m.</strong><br><strong>You will have the opportunity to meet other volunteers and staff and have a tour of the facilities.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"mailto:volunteer@horserescuespain.org\">volunteer@horserescuespain.org</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:embed {\"url\":\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xPA3F_LxazY\",\"type\":\"video\",\"providerNameSlug\":\"youtube\",\"responsive\":true,\"className\":\"wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xPA3F_LxazY\n</div></figure>\n<!-- /wp:embed -->','Volunteer with Us','','inherit','closed','closed','','151-revision-v1','','','2026-07-04 13:35:56','2026-07-04 13:35:56','',151,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?p=152',0,'revision','',0),(154,1,'2026-07-05 19:43:59','2026-07-04 13:36:58','','Adopt','','publish','closed','closed','','adopt-2','','','2026-07-05 19:43:59','2026-07-05 19:43:59','',0,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?p=154',2,'nav_menu_item','',0),(157,1,'2026-07-04 14:39:02','2026-07-04 14:39:02','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We rely on the support of animal lovers across the globe, and it is with your help that we continue to provide relief to horses, donkeys and ponies in need.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Enjoy some meaningful work at the rescue centre. Donate a few hours of your time to help us groom, feed and muck out the paddocks – there is always plenty to do.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our&nbsp;<strong>volunteer hours</strong>&nbsp;are:<br><strong>Mornings</strong><em><br></em>Monday to Friday – 8:30am to 11am<br>Saturday and Sunday – 9am to 11am<br>In addition, on the 1st Sunday of every month (except July + August) we need volunteers to show our visitors around from 10am to 2pm (10 to 12 or 12 to 2)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Evenings</strong><br>Times differ seasonally, usually a 2hr shift between 6pm and 9pm</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Please note that&nbsp;<strong>we do not have accommodation</strong>&nbsp;so volunteers from further afield would need to arrange their own accommodation and transport.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>If you would like to volunteer at ARCH could you please, for your initial visit to the stables, come either on a Wednesday or Saturday between 9.00 and 11.00 a.m.</strong><br><strong>You will have the opportunity to meet other volunteers and staff and have a tour of the facilities.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"mailto:volunteer@horserescuespain.org\">volunteer@horserescuespain.org</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:embed {\"url\":\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xPA3F_LxazY\",\"type\":\"video\",\"providerNameSlug\":\"youtube\",\"responsive\":true,\"className\":\"wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xPA3F_LxazY\n</div></figure>\n<!-- /wp:embed -->','Volunteer with Us','','inherit','closed','closed','','151-revision-v1','','','2026-07-04 14:39:02','2026-07-04 14:39:02','',151,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?p=157',0,'revision','',0),(239,1,'2026-07-04 14:55:33','2026-07-04 14:55:33','<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"textAlign\":\"center\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">We’re a small charity with limited resources, covering a huge region. We have no legal authority to act ourselves — we rely on the public reporting directly to Seprona or the Policía Local.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Report an Equine in Trouble','','publish','closed','closed','','reporting-abuse','','','2026-07-05 20:30:48','2026-07-05 20:30:48','',0,'http://localhost:8881/?page_id=239',0,'page','',0),(240,1,'2026-07-04 15:03:55','2026-07-04 15:03:55','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We wish we could investigate every complaint we receive, but we are a small charity with few volunteers and limited resources.&nbsp; Andalucía is a huge region of over 87.000 square kilometres, so it is physically impossible for us to attend to every report. We rely on the public to get involved to the full extent of their capability.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As a rescue centre, we do not have the necessary authorisation to take any action. We can usually only take action when requested to do so by Seprona or the Policía Local.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The person who has identified the case personally and has first-hand information needs to get involved and report all of the necessary information in order for the relevant authority to act accordingly.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How to report a case</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you have<strong>&nbsp;personally</strong>&nbsp;seen a neglected or mistreated or suspected abandoned equine that you are concerned about, please contact the relevant authority in the area:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">For Injured, mistreated or neglected equines – Responsibility of Seprona.</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Contact the Guardia Civil and request to report the case to Seprona. </li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>You can do this by using the AlertCops App – <a href=\"https://alertcops.ses.mir.es/publico/alertcops/en/\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://alertcops.ses.mir.es/publico/alertcops/en/\">click here</a> and download via Google Play or App Store, then select the ‘Maltrato Animal’ option)</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">For Abandoned equines – Responsibility of the local Ayuntamiento.</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Contact your Policia Local.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Please do not just share the post on social media</strong>&nbsp;as this has no benefit and can sometimes hamper investigations if the owner decides to move or hide the animal(s) in question.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Help Reporting</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you have a valid reason for not being able to contact the relevant authorities, or you believe that the animal’s life is in immediate danger and urgent action is required, we will intervene and report the matter on your behalf, but we will need as much information as possible – at least an exact and accurate location and full details of your concern with photos:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Details of <strong>why you are concerned</strong></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Equine details – (Horse/donkey/pony) colour&nbsp;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Name of owner&nbsp;</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>The <strong>location</strong> of the horse(s). The more information you can provide the better, even if the precise address is unknown. Please try to give additional location information such as a pin or google maps location.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Photos</strong> are very important, if you can, take some pictures of the equine(s) safely and without trespassing. These can then be sent to the authorities&nbsp;with the other details required.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Your contact details</strong>. You will need to provide your contact details in order for the authorities to contact you should they require more information. (These will remain anonymous if requested).</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Important considerations</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Throughout Spain, horses are managed and kept in many different ways. Sometimes we may not agree with the way in which a horse is kept but if its needs are being met and the horse is not suffering, then we are unlikely to be able to take any action. Whilst in an ideal world the animals would not be left all day in the sun, and it would be nice if they had the choice of sun or shade, many stand in the sun by choice all day anyway.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>We are unable to respond to welfare concerns reported to us through a ‘shared post’. Please send a private message.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>If you have already reported your concerns to the authorities and they have confirmed that they will be investigating, please do not contact other organisations and charities.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Please only report the matter if you have personally seen the equine(s) of concern. Unfortunately, we can’t take calls about second-hand information, including content seen on social media.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Hobbling is illegal in Spain and this should always be reported.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>If a horse seems thin, please ask yourself these questions:-<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Is it possible that it is old and has few teeth? Is it possible that it has been rescued and is being cared for? Is it possible that it has been sick? Is it thin by English or Spanish standards? Can you ask a neighbour, close to where the horse is kept, for details of who owns the horse and get some information?</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>In the summer water is usually only given to the animals in the morning and evening as if it is left in a bucket all day it will heat up and may cause colic.<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>It is not appropriate to feed and provide water to suspected equines in distress. You do not know if the equine is on any kind of medication or already receiving treatment that could be affected by unintended contravention of veterinary instruction. Furthermore, if Seprona respond to a report of a ‘neglected’ equine and find evidence that food and water is being provided they will not intervene. This may prejudice any chance of prosecuting an abusive owner.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Please only provide water or contact us directly if you have made every effort to report the matter through the relevant authorities and suspect that the animal’s life is in immediate danger and urgent action is required.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->','Reporting A Neglected, Mistreated or Abandoned Equine','','inherit','closed','closed','','239-revision-v1','','','2026-07-04 15:03:55','2026-07-04 15:03:55','',239,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?p=240',0,'revision','',0),(241,1,'2026-07-04 15:12:45','2026-07-04 15:12:45','','Arch-Yard-08-2019-scaled','','inherit','open','closed','','arch-yard-08-2019-scaled','','','2026-07-04 15:12:45','2026-07-04 15:12:45','',123,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Arch-Yard-08-2019-scaled-1.webp',0,'attachment','image/webp',0),(242,1,'2026-07-04 15:12:49','2026-07-04 15:12:49','','home-content','','inherit','closed','closed','','123-revision-v1','','','2026-07-04 15:12:49','2026-07-04 15:12:49','',123,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?p=242',0,'revision','',0),(246,1,'2026-07-04 16:09:50','2026-07-04 16:09:50','','Revoltosa','','inherit','open','closed','','revoltosa','','','2026-07-04 16:09:50','2026-07-04 16:09:50','',28,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Revoltosa.jpeg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(249,1,'2026-07-04 17:47:03','2026-07-04 17:47:03','<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"hero-sticker\"} -->\n<p id=\"hero-sticker\">Officially Utilidad Pública 🎉</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"hero-lede\"} -->\n<p id=\"hero-lede\">We\'re ARCH — a volunteer-powered rescue in Andalucía giving abandoned and abused equines a second chance at a good life. You\'ve been supporting us since 2009.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"hero-tag\"} -->\n<p id=\"hero-tag\">Star of the Month</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"anchor\":\"about-heading\"} -->\n<h2 id=\"about-heading\" class=\"wp-block-heading\">Transforming Equine Lives since 2009.</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"about-text-1\"} -->\n<p id=\"about-text-1\">We\'re the Andalusian Rescue Centre for Horses — registered as Centro Andalusí de Rescate de Caballos, but known locally as ARCH. Our mission is to <strong>rescue equines who have been abused, neglected, or abandoned</strong> – animals who have no one else to fight for their well-being. Most of our rescues come through SEPRONA (the animal welfare arm of the Guardia Civil), and abandoned animals are also brought in through the local police. Inevitably some of the older animals, or those with special needs, stay with us for a long time but <strong>the Centre is not a retirement home or a sanctuary</strong>, and we try to find suitable homes for all our rescue animals – the flow of deserving cases never stops, we have limited space, and it is hard to refuse to help.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"about-text-2\"} -->\n<p id=\"about-text-2\">Rescue is only part of the story. Once animals arrive at the Rescue Centre we work with SEPRONA, local equine vets and with our animal rights lawyer, <strong>Aritz Toribio</strong>, to take owners to court. This is a <strong>costly, frustrating and long-drawn-out process</strong> (cases can drag on for years and we rarely recoup anything like our costs). New animal cruelty legislation has been slow to filter through to judges and public prosecutors, but <strong>there have been some successful cases recently which give us hope</strong> that we may eventually win the fight for justice.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"contact-address\"} -->\n<p id=\"contact-address\">Viña Borrego (behind Miralmonte), A404, Alhaurín el Grande, Málaga, Spain</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"contact-hours\"} -->\n<p id=\"contact-hours\">Mon–Sat, 9:00–11:00am by appointment. First Sunday of the month, 10am–2pm (except July &amp; August).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"contact-email\"} -->\n<p id=\"contact-email\">info@horserescuespain.org</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"contact-footwear\"} -->\n<p id=\"contact-footwear\">Please wear closed shoes if you wish to groom or enter the paddocks.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"contact-cost\"} -->\n<p id=\"contact-cost\">Visits are free of charge, but any donations are gratefully received!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','home-content','','inherit','closed','closed','','123-revision-v1','','','2026-07-04 17:47:03','2026-07-04 17:47:03','',123,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?p=249',0,'revision','',0),(258,1,'2026-07-04 21:13:19','2026-07-04 21:13:19','','pexels-photo-2905358-1080444672','','inherit','open','closed','','pexels-photo-2905358-1080444672','','','2026-07-04 21:13:19','2026-07-04 21:13:19','',126,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/pexels-photo-2905358-1080444672.jpeg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(262,1,'2026-07-05 14:15:37','2026-07-05 14:15:37','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Every donation </strong>we receive goes <strong>directly to the equines</strong> at ARCH. With your help we can ensure each rescued horse, donkey and pony receives the treatment and rehabilitation they so desperately need.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>By making this donation, you acknowledge that it is a voluntary and irrevocable contribution. Donations received are non-refundable and will be used in full for the purposes of Centro Andalusí de Rescate de Caballos (ARCH).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ARCH is a non-profit organisation, <strong>registered with the Andalusian Regional Government</strong> (Junta de Andalucía) with <strong>number 8448</strong> and declared of benefit to the public [utilidad pública] on 25 March 2026, which means that all Spanish tax payers can claim their donation against tax.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The most cost efficient way to donate is via direct bank transfer to our bank account.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Donate','','inherit','closed','closed','','140-revision-v1','','','2026-07-05 14:15:37','2026-07-05 14:15:37','',140,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?p=262',0,'revision','',0),(263,1,'2026-07-05 14:21:15','2026-07-05 14:21:15','','Graciella','','publish','closed','closed','','graciella','','','2026-07-05 14:53:08','2026-07-05 14:53:08','',0,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?post_type=equine&#038;p=263',0,'equine','',0),(264,1,'2026-07-05 14:19:57','2026-07-05 14:19:57','','Victoria-4-before','','inherit','open','closed','','victoria-4-before','','','2026-07-05 14:19:57','2026-07-05 14:19:57','',263,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Victoria-4-before.jpeg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(265,1,'2026-07-05 14:20:57','2026-07-05 14:20:57','','Graciella-after','','inherit','open','closed','','graciella-after','','','2026-07-05 14:20:57','2026-07-05 14:20:57','',263,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Graciella-after.jpeg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(269,1,'2026-07-05 14:54:52','2026-07-05 14:54:52','<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"hero-sticker\"} -->\n<p id=\"hero-sticker\">Officially Utilidad Pública 🎉</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"hero-lede\"} -->\n<p id=\"hero-lede\">We\'re ARCH — a volunteer-powered rescue in Andalucía giving abandoned and abused equines a second chance at a good life. You\'ve been supporting us since 2009.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"hero-tag\"} -->\n<p id=\"hero-tag\">Star of the Month</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"anchor\":\"about-heading\"} -->\n<h2 id=\"about-heading\" class=\"wp-block-heading\">Transforming Equine Lives since 2009.</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"about-text-1\"} -->\n<p id=\"about-text-1\">We\'re the Andalusian Rescue Centre for Horses — registered as Centro Andalusí de Rescate de Caballos, but known locally as ARCH. Our mission is to <strong>rescue equines who have been abused, neglected, or abandoned</strong> – animals who have no one else to fight for their well-being. Most of our rescues come through SEPRONA (the animal welfare arm of the Guardia Civil), and abandoned animals are also brought in through the local police. Inevitably some of the older animals, or those with special needs, stay with us for a long time but <strong>the Centre is not a retirement home or a sanctuary</strong>, and we try to find suitable homes for all our rescue animals – the flow of deserving cases never stops, we have limited space, and it is hard to refuse to help.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"about-text-2\"} -->\n<p id=\"about-text-2\">Rescue is only part of the story. Once animals arrive at the Rescue Centre we work with SEPRONA, local equine vets and with our animal rights lawyer, <strong>Aritz Toribio</strong>, to take owners to court. This is a <strong>costly, frustrating and long-drawn-out process</strong> (cases can drag on for years and we rarely recoup anything like our costs). New animal cruelty legislation has been slow to filter through to judges and public prosecutors, but <strong>there have been some successful cases recently which give us hope</strong> that we may eventually win the fight for justice.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"contact-address\"} -->\n<p id=\"contact-address\">Viña Borrego (behind Miralmonte), A404, Alhaurín el Grande, Málaga, Spain</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"contact-hours\"} -->\n<p id=\"contact-hours\">Mon–Sat, 9:00–11:00am by appointment. First Sunday of the month, 10am–2pm (except July &amp; August).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"contact-email\"} -->\n<p id=\"contact-email\">info@horserescuespain.org</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"contact-footwear\"} -->\n<p id=\"contact-footwear\">Please wear closed shoes if you wish to groom or enter the paddocks.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"contact-cost\"} -->\n<p id=\"contact-cost\">Visits are free of charge, but any donations are gratefully received!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','home-content','','inherit','closed','closed','','123-revision-v1','','','2026-07-05 14:54:52','2026-07-05 14:54:52','',123,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?p=269',0,'revision','',0),(271,1,'2026-07-05 19:43:59','2026-07-05 15:12:17','','Volunteer','','publish','closed','closed','','volunteer','','','2026-07-05 19:43:59','2026-07-05 19:43:59','',0,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?p=271',4,'nav_menu_item','',0),(273,1,'2026-07-05 15:49:46','2026-07-05 15:49:46','','ARCH Shop','','publish','closed','closed','','arch-charity-shop','','','2026-07-05 15:50:49','2026-07-05 15:50:49','',0,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?page_id=273',0,'page','',0),(274,1,'2026-07-05 15:49:38','2026-07-05 15:49:38','','PrettyShop','','inherit','open','closed','','prettyshop','','','2026-07-05 15:49:38','2026-07-05 15:49:38','',273,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/PrettyShop.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(275,1,'2026-07-05 15:49:46','2026-07-05 15:49:46','','ARCH Charity Shop','','inherit','closed','closed','','273-revision-v1','','','2026-07-05 15:49:46','2026-07-05 15:49:46','',273,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?p=275',0,'revision','',0),(276,1,'2026-07-05 19:43:59','2026-07-05 15:50:08','','Shop','','publish','closed','closed','',276,'','','2026-07-05 19:43:59','2026-07-05 19:43:59','',0,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?p=276',5,'nav_menu_item','',0),(277,1,'2026-07-05 15:50:37','2026-07-05 15:50:37','','ARCH Shop','','inherit','closed','closed','','273-revision-v1','','','2026-07-05 15:50:37','2026-07-05 15:50:37','',273,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?p=277',0,'revision','',0),(279,1,'2026-07-05 17:10:30','2026-07-05 17:10:30','','Volunteer Day 1','','publish','closed','closed','','volunteer-day-1','','','2026-07-05 17:10:30','2026-07-05 17:10:30','',0,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?post_type=volunteer_photo&#038;p=279',0,'volunteer_photo','',0),(280,1,'2026-07-05 17:10:24','2026-07-05 17:10:24','','Screenshot 2026-07-05 at 17.43.00','','inherit','open','closed','','screenshot-2026-07-05-at-17-43-00','','','2026-07-05 17:10:24','2026-07-05 17:10:24','',279,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Screenshot-2026-07-05-at-17.43.00.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(281,1,'2026-07-05 17:10:26','2026-07-05 17:10:26','','Screenshot 2026-07-05 at 17.42.47','','inherit','open','closed','','screenshot-2026-07-05-at-17-42-47','','','2026-07-05 17:10:26','2026-07-05 17:10:26','',279,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Screenshot-2026-07-05-at-17.42.47.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(282,1,'2026-07-05 17:10:39','2026-07-05 17:10:39','','Volunteer Day 2025','','publish','closed','closed','','volunteer-day-2025','','','2026-07-05 17:10:45','2026-07-05 17:10:45','',0,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?post_type=volunteer_photo&#038;p=282',0,'volunteer_photo','',0),(283,1,'2026-07-05 17:11:31','2026-07-05 17:11:31','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Give one of our equines a home</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>At our rescue centre just outside Málaga, we try to rehome every rescue once they\'re suitably rehabilitated.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Adoption','','inherit','closed','closed','','68-revision-v1','','','2026-07-05 17:11:31','2026-07-05 17:11:31','',68,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?p=283',0,'revision','',0),(285,1,'2026-07-05 17:12:04','2026-07-05 17:12:04','<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Give one of our equines a home</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>At our rescue centre just outside Málaga, we try to rehome every rescue once they\'re suitably rehabilitated.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Adoption','','inherit','closed','closed','','68-revision-v1','','','2026-07-05 17:12:04','2026-07-05 17:12:04','',68,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?p=285',0,'revision','',0),(286,1,'2026-07-05 17:13:35','2026-07-05 17:13:35','','Volunteer with Us','','inherit','closed','closed','','151-revision-v1','','','2026-07-05 17:13:35','2026-07-05 17:13:35','',151,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?p=286',0,'revision','',0),(289,1,'2026-07-05 19:43:59','2026-07-05 19:32:25',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','',289,'','','2026-07-05 19:43:59','2026-07-05 19:43:59','',0,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?p=289',3,'nav_menu_item','',0),(290,1,'2026-07-05 19:43:59','2026-07-05 19:43:33','[gt-link lang=\"en\" label=\"English\" widget_look=\"flags\"]','English','','publish','closed','closed','','english','','','2026-07-05 19:43:59','2026-07-05 19:43:59','',0,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?p=290',8,'nav_menu_item','',0),(291,1,'2026-07-05 19:43:59','2026-07-05 19:43:33','[gt-link lang=\"es\" label=“Spanish\" widget_look=\"flags\"]','Spanish','','publish','closed','closed','','menu-item','','','2026-07-05 19:43:59','2026-07-05 19:43:59','',0,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?p=291',9,'nav_menu_item','',0),(293,1,'2026-07-05 20:07:26','2026-07-05 20:07:26','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We’re a small charity with limited resources, covering a huge region. We have no legal authority to act ourselves — we rely on the public reporting directly to Seprona or the Policía Local.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Helping an Equine in Trouble','','inherit','closed','closed','','239-revision-v1','','','2026-07-05 20:07:26','2026-07-05 20:07:26','',239,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?p=293',0,'revision','',0),(294,1,'2026-07-05 20:07:33','2026-07-05 20:07:33','<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"textAlign\":\"center\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">We’re a small charity with limited resources, covering a huge region. We have no legal authority to act ourselves — we rely on the public reporting directly to Seprona or the Policía Local.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Helping an Equine in Trouble','','inherit','closed','closed','','239-revision-v1','','','2026-07-05 20:07:33','2026-07-05 20:07:33','',239,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?p=294',0,'revision','',0),(297,1,'2026-07-05 20:27:36','2026-07-05 20:27:36','<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"textAlign\":\"center\"}}} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">We’re a small charity with limited resources, covering a huge region. We have no legal authority to act ourselves — we rely on the public reporting directly to Seprona or the Policía Local.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Report an Equine in Trouble','','inherit','closed','closed','','239-revision-v1','','','2026-07-05 20:27:36','2026-07-05 20:27:36','',239,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?p=297',0,'revision','',0),(298,1,'2026-07-05 20:29:26','2026-07-05 20:29:26','','Cookie Policy','','publish','closed','closed','','cookie-policy','','','2026-07-05 20:35:41','2026-07-05 20:35:41','',0,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?page_id=298',0,'page','',0),(299,1,'2026-07-05 20:29:26','2026-07-05 20:29:26','','Cookie Policy','','inherit','closed','closed','','298-revision-v1','','','2026-07-05 20:29:26','2026-07-05 20:29:26','',298,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?p=299',0,'revision','',0),(300,1,'2026-07-05 20:29:51','2026-07-05 20:29:51','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">In accordance with regulation (EU) 2016/679 of the European Parliament and of the Council of 27 April 2016</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Effective Date:</strong>&nbsp;27 May 2026</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">1. Introduction</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This Privacy Policy explains how Andalucian Rescue Centre for Horses (ARCH) (“ARCH”, “we”, “our”, or “us”) collects, uses, stores, and protects your personal information when you visit our website www.horserescuespain.org, contact us, donate, volunteer, adopt an equine, or otherwise interact with our services.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We are committed to protecting your privacy and handling your personal data transparently and in accordance with the European Union General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and applicable Spanish data protection laws.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">2. Who We Are</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ARCH (Centro Andalusí de Rescate de Caballos) is a registered non-profit organisation dedicated to rescuing, rehabilitating, and rehoming abandoned, abused, and neglected horses, ponies, and donkeys in Andalucía, Spain.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Contact Information</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Organisation:</strong>&nbsp;Centro Andalusí de Rescate de Caballos (ARCH)<br><strong>Represented by::</strong>&nbsp;Jill Newman-Rogers (President)<br><strong>Website:</strong>&nbsp;https://www.horserescuespain.org<br><strong>Email:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:info@horserescuespain.org\">info@horserescuespain.org</a><br><strong>Telephone:</strong>&nbsp;+34 711 070 099<br><strong>Location:</strong>&nbsp;Alhaurín el Grande, Málaga, Spain<br><strong>Spanish Tax ID (CIF):</strong>&nbsp;G92984368</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">3. What Information We Collect</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We may collect and process the following categories of personal information:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Information You Provide Directly</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Name</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Email address</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Telephone number</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Postal address</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Donation details</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Volunteer information</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Adoption application details</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Messages submitted through contact forms</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Newsletter subscription information</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sensitive or Additional Information</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In adoption or volunteer applications, we may collect additional information relevant to assessing suitability, such as:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Equine ownership experience</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Residency information</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Identification or legal residency details where required</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Home check consent information</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Automatically Collected Information</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When you use our website, we may automatically collect:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>IP address</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Browser type and device information</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Pages visited</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Cookies and analytics data</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Website usage statistics</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">4. How We Use Your Information</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We use your information to:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Respond to enquiries</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Process donations</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Manage volunteer applications</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Process equine adoption requests</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Send newsletters and updates</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Improve our website and services</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Organise events and fundraising activities</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Comply with legal obligations</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Protect the welfare of animals and support welfare investigations</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We only process your data where we have a lawful basis to do so under GDPR, including consent, contractual necessity, legal obligation, or legitimate interest.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">5. Reporting Animal Welfare Concerns</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you report a neglected, abandoned, or mistreated equine, we may collect:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Your contact details</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Photographs or evidence</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Location information</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Details relating to the welfare concern</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This information may be shared with relevant authorities such as SEPRONA, local police, veterinarians, or legal representatives where necessary to investigate animal welfare concerns.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">6. Donations and Payments</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you make a donation, payment information may be processed securely by third-party payment providers. ARCH does not store full payment card details on its servers.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Please review the privacy policies of any third-party payment processors before submitting payment information.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">7. Newsletter Communications</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you subscribe to our newsletter, we may send updates about:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Rescue activities</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Events</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Fundraising campaigns</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Volunteer opportunities</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Equines available for adoption</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You can unsubscribe at any time by clicking the unsubscribe link in any email or by contacting us directly. (<a href=\"https://www.horserescuespain.org/?utm_source=chatgpt.com\">horserescuespain.org</a>)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">8. Cookies</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our website may use cookies and similar technologies to:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Improve website functionality</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Analyse traffic and usage</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Remember user preferences</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You can control cookies through your browser settings. Disabling cookies may affect website functionality.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This site is protected by <a href=\"https://www.hCaptcha.com\">hCaptcha</a>. Its <a href=\"https://www.hcaptcha.com/privacy\">Privacy Policy</a> and <a href=\"https://www.hcaptcha.com/terms\">Terms of Service</a> apply except as noted in our <a href=\"https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/privacy-policy/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"300\">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">9. Sharing Your Information</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We do not sell your personal information.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We may share your data with:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Veterinary professionals</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Law enforcement or animal welfare authorities</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Payment processors</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Email newsletter providers</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Website hosting and technical service providers</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Legal advisers where necessary</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All third parties are expected to handle your information securely and lawfully.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">10. Data Retention</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We retain personal information only as long as necessary for:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>The purposes outlined in this policy</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Legal, accounting, or regulatory obligations</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Managing ongoing volunteer, adoption, or donation relationships</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When data is no longer required, it will be securely deleted or anonymised.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">11. Your Rights Under GDPR</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You have the right to:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Access your personal data</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Correct inaccurate information</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Request deletion of your data</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Restrict or object to processing</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Request data portability</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:info@horserescuespain.org\">info@horserescuespain.org</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">12. Data Security</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We take reasonable technical and organisational measures to protect your personal data against:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Unauthorised access</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Loss</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Misuse</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Disclosure</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Alteration or destruction</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>However, no internet transmission or storage system can be guaranteed completely secure.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">13. Third-Party Links</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our website may contain links to external websites, including social media pages, fundraising platforms, and partner organisations. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of external websites.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">14. Children’s Privacy</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our website and services are not directed toward children under 16 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children without appropriate parental consent.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">15. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically to reflect operational, legal, or regulatory changes. Updated versions will be posted on this page with a revised effective date.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">16. Contact Us</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or how your personal information is handled, please contact:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>ARCH – Centro Andalusí de Rescate de Caballos</strong><br>Email:&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:info@horserescuespain.org\">info@horserescuespain.org</a><br>Website:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.horserescuespain.org/?utm_source=chatgpt.com\">www.horserescuespain.org</a><br>Location: Alhaurín el Grande, Málaga, Spain (<a href=\"https://www.horserescuespain.org/?utm_source=chatgpt.com\">horserescuespain.org</a>)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Privacy Policy','','publish','closed','closed','','privacy-policy','','','2026-07-09 20:06:16','2026-07-09 20:06:16','',0,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?page_id=300',0,'page','',0),(301,1,'2026-07-05 20:29:51','2026-07-05 20:29:51','','Privacy Policy','','inherit','closed','closed','','300-revision-v1','','','2026-07-05 20:29:51','2026-07-05 20:29:51','',300,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?p=301',0,'revision','',0),(302,1,'2026-07-05 20:30:27','2026-07-05 20:30:27','','Privacy Policy','','inherit','closed','closed','','300-revision-v1','','','2026-07-05 20:30:27','2026-07-05 20:30:27','',300,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?p=302',0,'revision','',0),(303,1,'2026-07-05 20:35:04','2026-07-05 20:35:04','','Privacy Policy','','inherit','closed','closed','','300-revision-v1','','','2026-07-05 20:35:04','2026-07-05 20:35:04','',300,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?p=303',0,'revision','',0),(304,1,'2026-07-05 20:35:17','2026-07-05 20:35:17','','Cookie Policy','','inherit','closed','closed','','298-revision-v1','','','2026-07-05 20:35:17','2026-07-05 20:35:17','',298,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?p=304',0,'revision','',0),(306,1,'2026-07-05 20:38:54','2026-07-05 20:38:54','<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"hero-sticker\"} -->\n<p id=\"hero-sticker\">Officially Utilidad Pública 🎉</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"hero-lede\"} -->\n<p id=\"hero-lede\">We\'re ARCH — a volunteer-powered rescue in Andalucía giving abandoned and abused equines a second chance at a good life. You\'ve been supporting us since 2009.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"hero-tag\"} -->\n<p id=\"hero-tag\">Star of the Month</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"anchor\":\"about-heading\"} -->\n<h2 id=\"about-heading\" class=\"wp-block-heading\">Transforming Equine Lives since 2009.</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"about-text-1\"} -->\n<p id=\"about-text-1\">We\'re the Andalusian Rescue Centre for Horses — registered as Centro Andalusí de Rescate de Caballos, but known locally as ARCH. Our mission is to <strong>rescue equines who have been abused, neglected, or abandoned</strong> – animals who have no one else to fight for their well-being. Most of our rescues come through SEPRONA (the animal welfare arm of the Guardia Civil), and abandoned animals are also brought in through the local police. Inevitably some of the older animals, or those with special needs, stay with us for a long time but <strong>the Centre is not a retirement home or a sanctuary</strong>, and we try to find suitable homes for all our rescue animals – the flow of deserving cases never stops, we have limited space, and it is hard to refuse to help.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"about-text-2\"} -->\n<p id=\"about-text-2\">Rescue is only part of the story. Once animals arrive at the Rescue Centre we work with SEPRONA, local equine vets and with our animal rights lawyer, <strong>Aritz Toribio</strong>, to take owners to court. New animal cruelty legislation has been slow to filter through to judges and public prosecutors, but <strong>there have been some successful cases recently which give us hope</strong> that we may eventually win the fight for justice.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"contact-address\"} -->\n<p id=\"contact-address\">Viña Borrego (behind Miralmonte), A404, Alhaurín el Grande, Málaga, Spain</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"contact-hours\"} -->\n<p id=\"contact-hours\">Mon–Sat, 9:00–11:00am by appointment. First Sunday of the month, 10am–2pm (except July &amp; August).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"contact-email\"} -->\n<p id=\"contact-email\">info@horserescuespain.org</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"contact-footwear\"} -->\n<p id=\"contact-footwear\">Please wear closed shoes if you wish to groom or enter the paddocks.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"contact-cost\"} -->\n<p id=\"contact-cost\">Visits are free of charge, but any donations are gratefully received!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','home-content','','inherit','closed','closed','','123-revision-v1','','','2026-07-05 20:38:54','2026-07-05 20:38:54','',123,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?p=306',0,'revision','',0),(308,1,'2026-07-05 20:42:40','2026-07-05 20:42:40','','torero','','inherit','open','closed','','torero-2','','','2026-07-05 20:42:40','2026-07-05 20:42:40','',128,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/torero.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(310,1,'2026-07-06 07:30:32','2026-07-06 07:30:32','<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"hero-sticker\"} -->\n<p id=\"hero-sticker\">Officially Utilidad Pública 🎉</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"hero-lede\"} -->\n<p id=\"hero-lede\">We\'re ARCH — a volunteer-powered rescue in Andalucía giving abandoned and abused equines a second chance at a good life. You\'ve been supporting us since 2009.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"hero-tag\"} -->\n<p id=\"hero-tag\">Star of the Month</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"anchor\":\"about-heading\"} -->\n<h2 id=\"about-heading\" class=\"wp-block-heading\">Transforming Equine Lives since 2009.</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"about-text-1\"} -->\n<p id=\"about-text-1\">We\'re the Andalusian Rescue Centre for Horses — registered as Centro Andalusí de Rescate de Caballos, but known locally as ARCH. Our mission is to <strong>rescue equines who have been abused, neglected, or abandoned</strong> – animals who have no one else to fight for their well-being. Most of our rescues come through SEPRONA (the animal welfare arm of the Guardia Civil), and abandoned animals are also brought in through the local police. Inevitably some of the older animals, or those with special needs, stay with us for a long time but <strong>the Centre is not a retirement home or a sanctuary</strong>, and we try to find suitable homes for all our rescue animals.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"about-text-2\"} -->\n<p id=\"about-text-2\">Rescue is only part of the story. Once animals arrive at the Rescue Centre we work with SEPRONA, local equine vets and with our animal rights lawyer, <strong>Aritz Toribio</strong>, to take owners to court. New animal cruelty legislation has been slow to filter through to judges and public prosecutors, but <strong>there have been some successful cases recently which give us hope</strong> that we may eventually win the fight for justice.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"contact-address\"} -->\n<p id=\"contact-address\">Viña Borrego (behind Miralmonte), A404, Alhaurín el Grande, Málaga, Spain</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"contact-hours\"} -->\n<p id=\"contact-hours\">Mon–Sat, 9:00–11:00am by appointment. First Sunday of the month, 10am–2pm (except July &amp; August).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"contact-email\"} -->\n<p id=\"contact-email\">info@horserescuespain.org</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"contact-footwear\"} -->\n<p id=\"contact-footwear\">Please wear closed shoes if you wish to groom or enter the paddocks.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"contact-cost\"} -->\n<p id=\"contact-cost\">Visits are free of charge, but any donations are gratefully received!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','home-content','','inherit','closed','closed','','123-revision-v1','','','2026-07-06 07:30:32','2026-07-06 07:30:32','',123,'https://overtakefan.s2-tastewp.com/?p=310',0,'revision','',0),(311,1,'2026-07-06 15:08:21','2026-07-06 15:08:21','<!-- wp:paragraph {\"anchor\":\"hero-sticker\"} --